1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:02,790
No, no, no, no.
No, no, no.

2
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:05,830
Who is it?! Who dares to mess with me?

3
00:00:05,830 --> 00:00:08,630
What kind of jerk
dares to mess with a genius like me?

4
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:14,330
You...

5
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:16,960
Where did you get this evidence?!

6
00:00:17,290 --> 00:00:21,000
I have a friend who's good
at digging things up.

7
00:00:21,420 --> 00:00:22,920
We're not friends.

8
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:23,960
This is my job.

9
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:27,380
So you admit it.
This is the truth.

10
00:00:27,670 --> 00:00:30,290
What? Of course not.

11
00:00:30,630 --> 00:00:32,420
I didn't admit to anything.

12
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:33,420
What?

13
00:00:37,250 --> 00:00:38,380
No!

14
00:00:38,630 --> 00:00:39,830
It's not like that,
President Kurogane!

15
00:00:39,830 --> 00:00:41,630
It's these two.

16
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:43,580
These two witches.

17
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:44,880
It's a trap they set to frame me.

18
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:46,920
That's it!

19
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:48,290
Yes, yes, yes, that's it!

20
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:49,750
Trying to frame a genius like me.

21
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:50,790
It's a trap they set.

22
00:00:51,130 --> 00:00:52,130
It's a conspiracy.

23
00:00:52,580 --> 00:00:53,380
A conspiracy! It's a conspiracy!

24
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:55,000
This is no conspiracy.

25
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:57,920
President Kurogane!

26
00:00:58,830 --> 00:01:00,460
You're the president.

27
00:01:00,460 --> 00:01:01,880
How could you believe
a witch like her?

28
00:01:02,250 --> 00:01:03,420
She comes from a single-parent home.

29
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:05,040
A low-life commoner.
That witch.

30
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,630
Can you really trust anything she says?

31
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:07,630
I...

32
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:11,170
believe what this child says.

33
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,880
President Kurogane! Aaargh!

34
00:01:14,250 --> 00:01:17,500
This is beneath you,
President Kurogane.

35
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:18,920
Because she's my daughter.

36
00:01:19,630 --> 00:01:20,170
What?

37
00:01:20,460 --> 00:01:21,500
This child...

38
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,040
is my daughter.
